<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id065d462f-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s4673"><num value="4673">§ 4673.</num><heading> Funding</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The United States shall provide necessary funding to support the work of the Board, including with respect to translation services and personnel support.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id065d4630-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/pl/116/113/tVII/s733">Pub. L. 116–113, title VII, § 733</ref>, <date date="2020-01-29">Jan. 29, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/87">134 Stat. 87</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
